    "name": "Iniquity Survivors",
    "steam_appid": 2154830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/6e35c1ccb48ec1ea0b91b90d5b7e02a1.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=293 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/03b396d68076eae5b133921dd4a3c055.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/27ae7dbe3d281413b4245d3f291bf713.poster.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/27ae7dbe3d281413b4245d3f291bf713.webm?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/27ae7dbe3d281413b4245d3f291bf713.mp4?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Team up with your friends, search for a match online or play by yourself - <strong>Iniquity Survivors</strong> offers you the action-roguelite bullethell experience you always wanted to share with your friends.<br><br>Work together as a team to slay hordes of enemies or stand by yourself and butcher them all!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/6a3a3e00faa090783e0b3aeaec9610e8.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/fba6fa6ec1ef4276f087ff77ffed6b31.poster.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/fba6fa6ec1ef4276f087ff77ffed6b31.webm?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/fba6fa6ec1ef4276f087ff77ffed6b31.mp4?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each map consists of 2 Stages, 2 Intermissions and 1 Boss-Stage.<br>Reaching the Intermission Phase changes the map - be it a sudden snowstorm, thunderous storms or unbearable heat - you must find a way around the new challenge which the map has in for you. Buy powerups at the trading outpost and prepare wisely ...<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/e845e77e9adb5a8d1c25d163a24fbfce.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/44e482e55375cfaf97d25a92aff13825.poster.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/44e482e55375cfaf97d25a92aff13825.webm?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/44e482e55375cfaf97d25a92aff13825.mp4?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unlock and choose from a variety of runes for diverse and unique playstyles, providing playstyle-changing effects or granting a huge bonus to conquer even the hardest matches!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/8de52d73d5cedf0ceb6a5c9bd0e24055.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/267502ace9e8853975780aa357d6f1cc.poster.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/267502ace9e8853975780aa357d6f1cc.webm?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/267502ace9e8853975780aa357d6f1cc.mp4?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mill flowers, craft inks and potions to assist you in combat at the alchemists table! Research and unlock new potion recipes or upgrade the quality of your existing ones.<br><i>[NOTE: This feature is not available in the demo version!]</i><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/69e26fd67be55721e6205a945d8f205e.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/16b0aa27e130002ddb463f653063adb6.poster.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/16b0aa27e130002ddb463f653063adb6.webm?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/16b0aa27e130002ddb463f653063adb6.mp4?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect ressources from various maps, craft and upgrade powerful artifacts to increase your stats, gain powerful effects and make runs at higher difficulties easier (or even possible!)<br><i>[NOTE: This feature is not available in the demo version!]</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/34de494826075158570045cd3a6a269f.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/369099afe245e913982833c6a52b515c.poster.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/369099afe245e913982833c6a52b515c.webm?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/369099afe245e913982833c6a52b515c.mp4?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose between 3 powerful Upgrades after every wave and create your build as you want!<br>Heal or Tank for your team, play as a powerful Attackpower-based damage dealer, explore mysterious Magic with a focus on Spellpower or create your own broken build - with a great variety of unique powerups after each wave you can craft your own experience!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/c1c8e14dc85656ddb7302346bd1090bd.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/4715a143628a3f1ff3c52e103419aa0c.poster.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/4715a143628a3f1ff3c52e103419aa0c.webm?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/4715a143628a3f1ff3c52e103419aa0c.mp4?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Survive the waves of enemies thrown at you, gain strength and challenge various bosses in the final stage of each map. Bosses feature a great variety of abilities and mechanics, so prepare well, but defeating it will grant you great bonus rewards!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/862eeef283eebe3bbe3ce798b3b52f2d.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/af0b272f4b64245b4380ac4b8f3cef50.poster.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/af0b272f4b64245b4380ac4b8f3cef50.webm?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/af0b272f4b64245b4380ac4b8f3cef50.mp4?t=1706847489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Select torments, additional challenges, to make your runs harder and more interesting, granting you additional rewards when completing a run!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154830/extras/bc67a37bebc0b7971814c929a837d7a7.avif?t=1706847489\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><strong>Can I play solo or without friends?</strong><br><strong>Yes!</strong> There is a Singleplayer-Mode which allows you to play all by yourself.<br><br><strong>When is the full release?</strong><br>I do not want to disclose our final release date yet, so please stay patient!<br><br><strong>Will you support other languages and offer controller-support in the future?</strong><br>I might - depends a bit on how well the game is received :)<br><br><strong>Who is Rivenous Studio?</strong><br>I am a solo-dev who just likes making games.<br><br><strong>I have another question, where can I ask?</strong><br>You can always join the Iniquity Discord-Server () and ask your question right over there! I will be happy to answer your questions and listen to your feedback!",
